  <brief_title>A Study of Nivolumab Safety and Pharmacokinetics in Patients With Severe Sepsis or Septic Shock.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized, Double-Blind, Parallel Group Study to Evaluate the Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics and Pharmacodynamics of BMS-936558 (Nivolumab) in Participants With Severe Sepsis or Septic Shock.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
